## Limitations

The analysis is based on available online resources, which may not cover all perspectives or the latest research on the topic. The findings are also limited by the inherent biases present in the sources, which may emphasize either the positive or negative aspects of advertising. Further empirical research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of advertising's impact on society.